files.name: google
files.content:
<Button
        className="w-full"
        variant="outline"
        size="lg"
        onClick={() => handleOauth("google")}
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 326667 333333"
          shape-rendering="geometricPrecision"
          text-rendering="geometricPrecision"
          image-rendering="optimizeQuality"
          fill-rule="evenodd"
          clip-rule="evenodd"
          className="w-8 h-8"
        >
          {/* Google SVG Path */}
        </svg>
      </Button>
